# Canonical .dockerignore for Defra Node services.
#
# Keep the image lean and never leak local env into a built image.
#   - `.public` is the Vite build output; the Dockerfile rebuilds it, so exclude it
#     for SSR repos. Omit the line for API-only repos (they have no .public).
#   - `**/*.test.js` excludes test files from the image.
#   - `.env` MUST be excluded so local secrets never get baked into an image.
node_modules
Dockerfile
coverage
.public
**/*.test.js
.env
